General.Name: Ausmon Resources Ltd
General.Description: Ausmon Resources Limited, an exploration company, explores for, evaluates, and develops mineral resource properties in Australia. It explores for gold, silver, copper, cobalt, nickel, zinc, and other earth elements. Ausmon Resources Limited was incorporated in 2008 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
